# Google OAuth 2.0 Web application Client ID for Sign in with Google.
# Create in Google Cloud Console: APIs & Services > Credentials > Create OAuth client ID > Web application.
# Add Authorized JavaScript origins: http://localhost:5173 and your production URL (e.g. https://<user>.github.io/illo3d/).
# Do NOT add the Client Secret here — this app is client-only; the secret must never be in the frontend.
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=
